message: Hello, how can I assist you today?
I'm having trouble with my account.
Can you specify the problem you're encountering?
I can't seem to log in despite using the correct password.
Have you tried resetting your password through the 'Forgot Password' link?
Yes, I did, but I haven't received the reset email.
Let me check your account settings. Can you provide me your account email?
Thank you. I've sent a reset link to your email. Please check your inbox and the spam folder as well.
Got it, I'm able to reset my password now. Thanks for the help!
